iati-activity.description:
Selected number of kits is installed on a selected number of plots according to land size and cropping pattern;		
Selected number of technicians is trained on low cost/low pressure micro irrigation techniques;		
Selected number of farmers is trained on low cost/low pressure micro irrigation techniques;		
The performance of the new techniques for one season is monitored; 	
Conclusions and recommendation are drawn on the feasibility of implementation and the possibility of extrapolation to other basins.
